# Helm Command Reference
### Complete Command Table (Helm 3.15+)
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| Command              | Category   | Purpose                                  | When to use                            |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm create          | Scaffold   | Generate a new chart directory with      | Starting a new chart from scratch      |
|                      |            | best-practice structure                  |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm lint            | Validate   | Check chart for syntax errors and        | In CI before every release; locally    |
|                      |            | best-practice violations                 | before every commit                   |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm template        | Render     | Render templates client-side without     | Inspect what will be deployed; debug  |
|                      |            | submitting to cluster                    | template logic                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm install         | Deploy     | Install a chart as a new named release   | First deployment of an application    |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm upgrade         | Deploy     | Upgrade an existing release or install   | All subsequent deployments            |
|                      |            | if not present                           |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm upgrade --install | Deploy   | Idempotent install-or-upgrade            | CI pipelines — works on first run and |
|                      |            |                                          | all subsequent runs                   |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm rollback        | Recovery   | Revert a release to a previous revision  | Incident response; failed upgrade     |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm uninstall       | Lifecycle  | Delete a release and all its managed     | Decommissioning; cleanup              |
|                      |            | resources                                |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm list            | Inspect    | List all releases in a namespace or      | Operational overview                  |
|                      |            | cluster                                  |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm status          | Inspect    | Show deployment status of a specific     | Verify a release is healthy           |
|                      |            | release                                  |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm get manifest    | Inspect    | Retrieve the rendered manifests from a   | Post-incident analysis; compare       |
|                      |            | specific revision                        | revisions                             |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm get values      | Inspect    | Retrieve the values used for a specific  | Audit what config was applied         |
|                      |            | revision                                |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm get all         | Inspect    | Retrieve manifest + values + notes for   | Full release state dump               |
|                      |            | a revision                              |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm history         | Audit      | Show revision history for a release      | Audit trail; find revision to roll    |
|                      |            |                                          | back to                               |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm repo add        | Registry   | Register a chart repository              | Adding community or private chart     |
|                      |            |                                          | sources                               |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm repo update     | Registry   | Refresh cached chart index from all       | Before helm search or helm pull       |
|                      |            | registered repos                         |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm repo list       | Registry   | List all registered chart repositories    | Inventory of chart sources            |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm search repo     | Discovery  | Search registered repositories for charts| Finding available charts and versions |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm search hub      | Discovery  | Search Artifact Hub (public charts)      | Finding community charts              |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm pull            | Fetch      | Download a chart tarball from a          | Inspect a chart locally; air-gapped   |
|                      |            | repository                              | deployments                          |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm show chart      | Inspect    | Display Chart.yaml from a chart          | View chart metadata and version       |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm show values     | Inspect    | Display default values.yaml from a       | Understand configurable parameters    |
|                      |            | chart                                   |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm show readme     | Inspect    | Display chart README                    | Documentation                         |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm dependency update | Dependencies | Download chart dependencies declared in | Before building a chart with          |
|                      |            | Chart.yaml                              | sub-charts                           |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm dependency build | Dependencies | Build dependencies from Chart.lock       | Reproducible builds from lockfile     |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm package         | Publish    | Package a chart directory into a .tgz    | CI publish step; chart release       |
|                      |            | artefact                                |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm test            | Test       | Execute test hooks defined in           | Post-deploy smoke testing             |
|                      |            | templates/tests/                        |                                        |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm diff upgrade    | Safety     | Show the diff of what would change      | Mandatory before every production    |
|                      |            | before applying                         | upgrade                               |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm plugin install  | Extension  | Install a Helm plugin                   | Adding helm-diff, helm-unittest,      |
|                      |            |                                         | helm-secrets                          |
+----------------------+------------+------------------------------------------+----------------------------------------+
| helm env             | Debug      | Print Helm environment variables and    | Diagnosing configuration issues       |
|                      |            | paths                                   |                                        |
